OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FA report has revealed the cost of
OL,8,Frepairing potholes across the South
OL,9,FWest is at a record high.
OL,11,FAfter months of heavy rain, the repair
OL,12,Fcost has soared to #2.9 billion
OL,13,Faccording to the Asphalt Industry
OL,14,FAlliance, which represents road-makers.
OL,16,FThe report says only half of the
OL,17,Fregion's roads are in a good
OL,18,Fcondition, with one in six of them
OL,19,Fneeding urgent repairs in the next
OL,20,Ffive years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
