CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report says although 1.9 million
OL,8,Fpotholes were filled nationally over
OL,9,Fthe last year, authorities would have
OL,10,Fneeded, on average, an extra #8.1
OL,11,Fmillion each last year to maintain
OL,12,Ftheir network to their own target
OL,13,Fconditions and prevent further decline.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FMalcolm Simms, Director of the Asphalt
OL,8,FIndustry Alliance said: "I think any
OL,9,Froad user can tell you the effects on
OL,10,Ftheir day to day journeys, it's
OL,11,Fincreasingly uncomfortable,
OL,12,Fincreasingly dangerous, damage to
OL,13,Fwheels, tyres, all sorts of
OL,14,Funnecessary expense to the road user.
OL,16,F"With a particularly large road
OL,17,Fnetwork in the South West,
OL,18,Fparticularly in Devon and Cornwall,
OL,19,Fthe challenge is just getting bigger
OL,20,Fand bigger every year.
OL,26,@pD@YOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"What we're calling for is that the
OL,8,FGovernment invests and invests soon,
OL,9,Fthey have made announcements of #7.3
OL,10,Fbillion over the next 4 years but
OL,11,Fthat's weighted towards the back end,
OL,12,Ftowards 2030, so what we're saying is
OL,13,Fbring that funding forward, do the
OL,14,Fwork now, because the roads are
OL,15,Fdeteriorating while we wait for the
OL,16,Fmoney to come through."
OL,18,FBen Thornbury from Malmesbury says he
OL,19,Fis so frustrated by potholes that he
OL,20,Fhas turned to humour by filling them
OL,21,Fin or using them as games.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
