CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"I'm planting flowers in the potholes
OL,8,Fto raise awareness of the issue", he
OL,9,Ftold ITV News.
OL,11,F"The councils don't take action about
OL,12,Fpotholes, so sometimes it takes me
OL,13,Fhaving to do different campaigns to
OL,14,Fget them to resurface the road or fill
OL,15,Fthe potholes in.
OL,17,F"I've done pothole golf, I've done
OL,18,Fpothole fishing and the other day it
OL,19,Fwas pothole bowling and funnily enough
OL,20,Fthat road got resurfaced about two
OL,21,Fweeks later."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
