OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIn a statement Wiltshire Council said:
OL,8,F"Since January, we have received more
OL,9,Fthan 21,400 pothole reports and we are
OL,10,Fworking hard to repair these defects
OL,11,Fas quickly as possible.
OL,13,F"So far this year, we have repaired
OL,14,Fmore than 5,163 potholes.
OL,16,F"Before the recent spell of wet and
OL,17,Fcold weather, Wiltshire had seen a 28%
OL,18,Freduction in pothole reports in 2025
OL,19,Fcompared with 2024.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"While the recent rise in pothole
OL,8,Fnumbers reflects a national trend, the
OL,9,FDepartment for Transport considers
OL,10,FWiltshire to be one of the better-
OL,11,Fperforming authorities."
OL,13,FSimon Williams from the RAC said:
OL,14,F"People are mentioning potholes when
OL,15,Fthey report their breakdown to us as
OL,16,Fmuch as 330 in a single day, last year
OL,17,Fit was 43 a day. That's because
OL,18,Fpotholes have been hidden in puddles
OL,19,Fand drivers haven't had a clue they
OL,20,Fwere there.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Because of poor maintenance of local
OL,8,Froads water has made its way into
OL,9,Fcracks in the roads, frozen during the
OL,10,Fcold weather, expanded and caused more
OL,11,Fpotholes.
OL,13,F"The Government has given more money
OL,14,Fto councils in England than ever
OL,15,Fbefore and are now agreeing to five
OL,16,Fyear funding cycles but the most
OL,17,Fimportant thing to do is preventative
OL,18,Fmaintenance. Surface dressing seals
OL,19,Fthe cracks in the road, stops water
OL,20,Fgetting in and prevents potholes
OL,21,Fforming.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
