OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"The state of our roads is one of the
OL,8,Fbiggest concerns drivers have.
OL,9,FPotholes are not only a danger to
OL,10,Fpeople, cyclists and motorcyclists but
OL,11,Fthey can cause expensive damage to
OL,12,Fvehicles."
OL,14,FA Department for Transport
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "This report
OL,16,Frightly highlights the need to improve
OL,17,Four roads. That's why, after years of
OL,18,Funderinvestment, we're providing a
OL,19,Frecord #7.3 billion in long-term
OL,20,Ffunding to help councils resurface
OL,21,Froads and fix the pothole plague.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
