PN,43610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1773850286
OL,3,CCost of pothole repairs across the
OL,4,CSouth West hits record levels, says
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"#1.5bn of this will go to councils in
OL,8,Fthe South West over the next four
OL,9,Fyears, giving them the long term
OL,10,Fcertainty they need to plan and
OL,11,Fdeliver repairs."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
